Description: Credential Management for DBIx::Class
 DBIx::Class::Schema::Config is a subclass of DBIx::Class::Schema that
 allows the loading of credentials & configuration from a file. The
 actual code itself would only need to know about the name used in the
 configuration file. This aims to make it simpler for operations teams
 to manage database credentials.
